-Son of a bitch.

518
00:35:14,198 --> 00:35:15,949
Nothin's over
while I'm breathin'.

519
00:35:17,492 --> 00:35:18,827
I kinda hoped you'd say that.

520
00:35:36,136 --> 00:35:37,346
No, no, you stay
with the ikran.

521
00:35:37,513 --> 00:35:38,597
But, Dad...

522
00:35:38,722 --> 00:35:39,431
