Keep going!

2222
02:46:32,242 --> 02:46:33,243
This way,
this way!

2223
02:46:33,744 --> 02:46:34,411
Okay.

2224
02:46:34,578 --> 02:46:35,204
Go!

2225
02:46:39,333 --> 02:46:41,335
Open it!

2226
02:46:43,295 --> 02:46:44,379
Mom!

2227
02:46:47,424 --> 02:46:48,425
Come on!

2228
02:46:57,976 --> 02:46:58,977
Go, Tuk!

