slow your heart down.

2272
02:52:20,924 --> 02:52:22,092
Be real calm.

2273
02:52:23,427 --> 02:52:24,678
Breathe
from here.

2274
02:52:24,845 --> 02:52:26,430
Hey, breathe from here.

2275
02:52:39,985 --> 02:52:41,320
The way of water has no...

2276
02:52:41,445 --> 02:52:42,738
