Nothing is ever lost.

2330
03:00:16,108 --> 03:00:17,109
Neteyam!

2331
03:00:17,734 --> 03:00:18,944
Neteyam!

2332
03:00:39,006 --> 03:00:40,257
My family and I...

2333
